title: Usage Accounting
headline: Usage Accounting | Track AI Model Usage with OpenRouter
canonical-url: https://openrouter.ai/docs/guides/administration/usage-accounting
og:site_name: OpenRouter Documentation
og:title: Usage Accounting - Track AI Model Token Usage
og:description: Learn how to track AI model usage including prompt tokens, completion tokens, and cached tokens without additional API calls.
og:image:width: 1200
og:image:height: 630
twitter:card: summary_large_image
